Claude Code Harness
===================

This project is a generalized, portable derivative of a private harness
originally developed for a specific script-generation project.

Upstream reference:
- Chachamaru127/claude-code-harness v3.1.0 (guardrail rule structure,
  skill taxonomy, and agent composition were informed by this work)

All project-specific references (YouTube Shorts pipeline, OpenAI script
generation, proprietary annotated data) have been removed or parameterized
in this distribution. Guardrail rules R01-R09, R12, R13 are domain-neutral.
Rules R10 and R11 are fully parameterized via harness.config.json.

